                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17910608-43-defend479 t17910608-43-punish258"></join>
               Whipped
            </rs> and <rs id="t17910608-43-punish259" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17910608-43-punish259" type="punishmentCategory" value="imprison"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17910608-43-defend479 t17910608-43-punish259"></join>
               imprisoned six months
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
